thread.title: Customer Terry
thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by Customer Terry

author: Customer Terry
title: Customer Terry
text: I just want to say that Vital Choice has the best fish I have ever had. The Wild King Salmon is so juicy and delicious. The salmon burgers are great for quick dinners and also taste delicious. Don't miss out on the wonderful dark chocolate. Rest assured that anything you buy is top quality.
